Welcome to Calantro, the RuneScape private server brought to you by kush and george. We have over 30 registered members, playable 24/7.Here at Colantro we take a different approach the other generic servers you come across. Security and stability are very important to us, that's why we make sure we are the best around at offering this.In regard to content, Colantro is a spawn server,We also have some of the most enjoyable Pking around, our Wilderness zones are always packed with pkers.
